hadiths[8]{hadithnumber,text}:
2125,"unhoney Barira ko kharidney (aur azad karney (ka irada kya to Barira key ghar walon ney wala ( meeras ( ki shart rakhi , Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' wala ( meeras (ka haq usi ko hasil hai jo qeemat ada karey ya azad karney ki nemat ka Malik ho '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai."
2126,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney wala key bechney aur usey hiba karney sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- hum isey sirf Abdullah bin Dinar key wastey sey ibne-Umar ki riwayat sey jantey hain, aur wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain, aap ney wala bechney aur usey hiba karney sey mana farmaya. Shoba, Sufiyan Sory aur Malik bin Anas ney bhi ye hadees Abdullah bin Dinar sey riwayat hai, Shoba sey marvi hai, unhoney kaha : meri khaahish thi ke Abdullah bin Dinar is hadees ko bayan kartey waqt mujhey ijazat dey detey aur main khada ho kar unka sar choom leta, 3- Yahya bin Sulaim ney is hadees ki riwayat kartey waqt sanad yun bayan ki hai (عن عبيد الله بن عمر an نافع an ابن عمر an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) lekin is sanad mein weham hai aur ye weham Yahya bin saleem ki janib sey huwa hai, sahih sanad yun hai عن عبيد الله بن عمر an عبد الله بن دينار an ابن عمر an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) Ubedullah bin umr sey isi tarah kaee logon ney riwayat ki hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Ubedullah bin Dinar is hadees ki riwayat karney mein munfarid hain."
2127,"Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney hamarey darmiyan khutba diya aur kaha : jo kehta hai ke hamarey paas Allah ki kitab aur us sahifey, jiskey andar oonton ki Umr aur zakhmon key ehkam hain, key ilawa koi aur chiz hai jisey hum padhtey hain to wo jhoot kehta hai padhi. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha is sahifey mein ye bhi hai ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''eir sey ley kar soor tak Madina Haram hai padhi. jo shakhs uskey andar koi bidat ejaad karey ya bidat ejaad karney waley ko panah dey , is par Allah , uskey farishtey aur tamam logon ki lanat ho, qiyamat key din Allah Taala us aadmi ki na koi farz ibadat qubul kerega aur na nafl aur jo shakhs doosrey key baap ki taraf apni nisbat karey ya apney azad karney waley key ilawa ko apna Malik banaey uskey ooper Allah , uskey farishtey aur tamam logon ki lanat ho, uski na farz ibadat qubul hogi aur na nafl , musalmanon ki taraf sey di janey wali panah eik hai unka maamuli shakhs bhi us panah ka Malik hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- baaz logon ney (عن الأعمش an إبراهيم التيمي an الحارث بن سويد an علي) ki sanad sey usi jaisi hadees riwayat ki hai, 3- ye hadees kaee sanadon sey Ali key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aai hai."
2128,"bani Fazara key eik aadmi ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! meri biwi sey eik kaalaa bacha paida huwa hai? Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney us sey puchha : '' tumharey paas oont hain? '' usney kaha : haan , aap ney puchha : '' wo kis rang key hain? '' usney kaha : surkh, aap ney puchha : ''kya is mein koi matmeley rang ka bhi hai? '' usney kaha : haan, us main eik khaakastri rang ka bhi hai. aap ney puchha : '' wo kahan sey aaya ? '' usney kaha : shayad wo koi khandani rag khinch laya hoga, aap ney farmaya : '' us ladkey ney bhi shayad koi khandani rag khinch li ho aur kalay rang ka ho ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2129,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam khushi khushi unkey paas tashrif laye, aap key chehrey key khutoot chamak rahey they, aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum ney dekha nahin, abhi abhi Mujazzaz ney Zaid bin Harisa aur Usama bin Zaid ko dekh kar kaha hai ke ye qadam (yani unka rishta) eik doosrey sey hain padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ibn Uena ney ye hadees (عن الزهري an عروة an عائشة) ki sanad sey riwayat ki hai. aur is mein ye izafa kya hai, aap ney farmaya : ''kya tum ney nahin dekha ke Mujazzaz, Zaid bin Harisa aur Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) key paas sey guzra, us waqt wo dono apna sar dhaanpey huye they aur unkey pair khuley huye they to usney kaha : un qadmon (ka rishta) eik doosrey sey hain, 3- isi tarah hum sey Saeed bin Abdur-Rehman aur kaee logon ney ye hadees (عن سفيان بن عيينة هذا الحديث an الزهري an عروة an عائشة) ki sanad sey bayan ki hai, ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 4- baaz ehle-ilm ney is hadees sey qiyaafa key moatabar honey par istidlaal kya hai."
2130,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum log eik doosrey ko hadiya diya karo, isliye ke hadiya dil ki kadurat ko door karta hai, koi padausan apni padausan key hadiya ko haqeer na samjhey agar-che wo bakri key khur ka eik tukda hi kyon na ho''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai, 2- abu-Ma'shar ka naam najeeh hai wo bani-Hashim key ( azad karda ( ghulam hain, unkey hafizey key talluq sey baaz ehle-ilm ney unkey barey mein kalam kya hai"
2131,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs hadiya dey kar phir wapis ley ley uski misal us kuttey ki tarah hai jo khaata rahey yahan tak ke jab uska pet bhar jaey to qai karey , phir usey chaat ley ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein ibne-Abbas aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2132,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' kisi aadmi key liye jayez nahin ke koi hadiya dey , phir usey wapis ley ley , siwaye baap key jo apney betey ko deta hai) wo usey wapis ley sakta hai) aur jo shakhs koi Atiya dey phir wapis ley ley uski misal us kuttey ki tarah hai jo khaata rahey yahan tak ke jab aasooda ho jaey to qai karey , phir apna qai kha ley ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Shafai kehtey hain : kisi hadiya deney waley key liye jayez nahin ke hadiya wapis ley ley siwaye baap key , kyonkey uskey liye jayez hai ke jo hadiya apney betey ko diya hai usey wapis ley ley , unhoney isi hadees sey istidlaal kya hai."
